text.inkscape:label: Size explanation
text.tspan: SVG viewbox of each icon file: 32x32
Size of the icon's visual elements: 16x16 (that is, there's a padding of 8 in the SVG file, with small overflow allowed)
In the toolbar, the 32x32 icons are next to each other without gaps. So there's a perceptual gap of 16 between icons.
The whole toolbar has a padding of 8, so there's a perceptual gap of 16 between the icon and the toolbar border.
Thin lines should have a width of 1. Thick lines should have a width of 2.
Small points should have a diameter of 3. Large points should have a diameter of 4.
